=80=99s actually deeply underperforming the Nasdaq this year.=E2=80=9D=C2=
=A0
=E2=80=9CAhh,=E2=80=9D you=E2=80=99d reply, =E2=80=9CUnderperforming. Now I=
 know what company you=E2=80=99re talking about. Slack!=E2=80=9D
From Day 1, I=E2=80=99ve known Slack was a long-term play. It acquires cust=
omers slowly, but is incredibly good at retaining and growing with them onc=
e they=E2=80=99re hooked. That takes time to pay off. I=E2=80=99ve owned sh=
ares in Slack since the day it IPO=E2=80=99d direct listed [https://email.m=
g2.substack.com/c/eJxFkE2OhCAQhU_T7DQCSnTBYjZ9DcNPqaQRDJRte_tBe5JJCAWvinrFZ=
