rkflows. It=E2=80=99s maniacally focused on making communication more effec=
tive.=C2=A0
It does that by working on the little things that make the overall experien=
ce of using Slack delightful. For example, it was the first workplace chat =
tool to sync your place in a channel across devices, meaning that the conve=
rsation on the desktop app would pick up where you left off on mobile. It p=
uts an enormous amount of thought into something as simple as when to send =
which notifications, as exemplified in this now-famous notification decisio=
